        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDear All, \nThis issue can be easily overcome by adding \n\"USER root\" just under\nFROM nexus3.onap.org:10001/onap/integration-java11:latest\n\nafter that, the question may be, what uid could be assigned for the user so (possibly\nuser onap from integration-java11 container takes 1000). So, so user and group can be i.e. 1001 or 999.\n\nAt the end of dockerfile you can switch user to SO or ONAP. \nAfter that container \"nexus3.onap.org:10001/onap/integration-java11:latest\" can be successfully applied to the base image",
